transArray.content: I booked a superior double room. The hotel window faces the community and it is very quiet. If you stay on the seventh floor, you can also see the small park to the east. The surrounding environment is very good! The waiters in the store are also very good and very enthusiastic. Very satisfied
Dear guest, thank you very much for choosing. Summer has the late glow. Just like the little guy who comes late, everyone is smiling. I love you, little guy.
